     * Hb≥90g/L
     * ANC≥1.5×10\^9/L; LC≥0.5×10\^9/L;
     * PLT≥100×10\^9/L;
     * WBC≥3.0×10\^9/L, ≤15×10\^9/L;
  2. Blood chemistry (no blood transfusion or albumin within 7 days prior to screening):

     * ALT, AST≤1.5 ULN;
     * ALP≤2.5 ULN;
     * TBIL≤1.5 ULN;
     * Cr≤1.5 ULN, CrCL≥50 mL/min;
